<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>304</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa chieh dinga nei sawl na ta phawt achun,
 Tangsangpen leh tuipi kinawk kal himahleh;
 Na thu leh Kraws vaka nei thuom phawt chun,
 Na hehpihna thu hi gen zel ingka

[V2]
 Chieh in sempan ngalin nite bei mang zing,
 Kalvari tatna mak henailo te kawmah;
 Na tawhna ta phawt chu na gam hizel ina,
 Hattak leh hangtak in umphawt mai in.

[V3]
 2. Setan gallien chu lau loin nawh pai zelin,
 Tawpchana na kawma umdi'n thu ka hun tiem;
 Thu ka hun pie hila bangmah lau ki'n,
 Hattak leh hang takin um phawt mai in.

[V4]
 3. Ka hukdamna Zion tang achun hun puiin,
 Amau dingin mun nuom leh chawlhna ka guonggalh;
 Hattak leh hangtakin va gen zelin,
 Na kipahman Lallukhuk hawih ina.</lyrics>
<title>Hattak Leh Hangtak in</title>
</song>